name: THE WOVEN PENTAGRAM GIF - CHEQUERED EDITION
description:
The pentagram is a symbol with magical associations used as far back as ancient Greece and Babylonia. This specific design is very unique as there are 25 pentagrams (each woven within a circle) placed across a chequered background which alternates.

The dimensions of this design are as follows: 1,200 pixels x 1,200 pixels

The woven pentagram was built using geometric proofs and mathematical equations. It was completed on the 27th April 2018.
